@0 = ~Wait!! I am looking for fairy dust. Would you know where I can find some?~
@1 = ~Usually we do not share this kind of things, but in return for what you did for us, I will ask this dust to our forest sisters. Wait here.~
@2 = ~There you go. This is a rare gift we’re giving you, so I hope you’ll put it to good use.~
@3 = ~Don't worry about that.~
